name: Last One Left (Eggs)
description:
Be the last egg left! At the start of the game, you're randomly assigned a player Egg. One by one, as the eggs get take, choose whether you want to move spots or stay where you are - either way, chancing becoming the next to be picked. Will you be a Winner or will you get Wasted?

Game: Last One Left: Egg

For: https://itch.io/jam/weekly-game-jam-149

All 3D assets are free models from TurboSquid.
